main: ^I have recently been thinking of my youth & how we would play old games with my dad, before all this android nonsense
^My favorite memory is when he showed me his favorite game Contra, how he beat it fairly, but for me (as I was very small) he would put in a cheat code.
^I still remember the code: up, up, down, down, left, right,left, right, B, A, Start
